    %% Core Platform Dependencies
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| Dashboard
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| NotebookCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| KServe
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| ModelMesh
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| ODHModelCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| DSP
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| KubeRay
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| CodeFlare
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| Kueue
    RHODSOp -->|deploys & manages| TrustyAI

    %% Dashboard Integration
    Dashboard -->|creates Notebook CRs| NotebookCtrl
    Dashboard -->|creates InferenceService CRs| KServe
    Dashboard -->|creates DSPA CRs| DSP
    Dashboard -->|queries metrics| Monitoring

    %% Model Serving Dependencies
    KServe -->|requires| Knative
    KServe -->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -->|uses| CertManager
    KServe -->|integrates with| ODHModelCtrl
    ModelMesh -->|integrates with| ODHModelCtrl
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates Routes| K8sAPI
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates VirtualServices| ServiceMesh

    %% Distributed Computing Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|creates Ray clusters| K8sAPI
    CodeFlare -->|secures| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|adds OAuth| OAuth
    CodeFlare -->|adds mTLS| ServiceMesh
    Kueue -->|manages resources for| KubeRay
    Kueue -.->|can manage| DSP

    %% Monitoring Integration
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| ModelMesh
    TrustyAI -->|exposes metrics to| Monitoring

    %% Platform Infrastructure Dependencies
    RHODSOp -->|watches CRDs| K8sAPI
    RHODSOp -->|configures| ServiceMesh
    Dashboard -->|authenticates via| OAuth
    NotebookCtrl -->|uses| OAuth
    ModelMesh -->|uses| OAuth
    DSP -->|uses| OAuth
    CodeFlare -->|uses| OAuth

    %% Certificate Management
    KServe -->|webhook certs| CertManager
    ModelMesh -->|webhook certs| CertManager
    Kueue -->|webhook certs| CertManager
    Dashboard -->|proxy TLS| ServiceCA
    ModelMesh -->|proxy TLS| ServiceCA
    DSP -->|proxy TLS| ServiceCA

    %% External Storage Dependencies
    KServe -->|model artifacts| S3
    ModelMesh -->|model artifacts| S3
    DSP -->|pipeline data| S3
    NotebookCtrl -->|datasets| S3
    KubeRay -->|checkpoints| S3

    DSP -->|pipeline metadata| ExternalDB

    %% Container Images
    RHODSOp -->|pulls images| Registry
    NotebookCtrl -->|pulls images| Registry
    WorkbenchImages -->|from| Registry
    KServe -->|pulls runtime images| Registry
    ModelMesh -->|pulls runtime images| Registry

    %% Package Dependencies
    WorkbenchImages -->|installs packages| PackageRepos

    %% Monitoring Dependencies
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| RHODSOp
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| Dashboard
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| NotebookCtrl
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| KServe
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| ModelMesh
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| ODHModelCtrl
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| DSP
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| KubeRay
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| CodeFlare
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| Kueue
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| TrustyAI

